name: hora do sol
description:
a primavera chegou, hora de colocar a cara no sol novamente e deixar tudo florescer! fotografia tirada dentro de um cinema abandonado no bairro Vila Morro Grande na zona norte de São Paulo.
mint especial para o evento #springoBRjkt.

the spring has arrived, it's time to put your face in the sun again and let it all bloom! photograph was taken inside an abandoned movie theater in the Vila Morro Grande neighborhood, north of São Paulo.
special mint for the #springoBRjkt event.
